com.interpss.core.algo.planning

Interface PlanningPeriodAclfNet

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PlanningPeriodAclfNetImpl

    public interface PlanningPeriodAclfNet
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Period Aclf Net'. Planning time period AclfNetwork class

    The following features are supported:

    • No
    • Start Time
    • End Time
    • Aclf Net
    • Parent Container
    See Also:
    PlanningAlgorithmPackage.getPlanningPeriodAclfNet()
